<function>

access:   public

name: __construct

param: array, $config, NULL

return: Solar_Cache_Memcache

</function>

Constructor.

* Parameters:

 * array //$config//: User-provided configuration values.

* Returns Solar_Cache_Memcache: Solar_Cache_Memcache instance

Constructor.

Config keys are:

: \\host\\ : (string) The hostname of the memcached server, default 'localhost' 

: \\port\\ : (int) The port number for the memcached server, default 11211 

: \\life\\ : (int) The lifetime of each cache entry in seconds, default 60 (1 minute)